Class Lecturer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Lecturer

  • public class Lecturer
extends java.lang.Object
    Lecturer is a class to define a lecturer at typical School

    Lecturer has an id, First Name, Last Name, Phone number and an Address.

    Date 15/11/16

    Kamal Karwal
